    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Some 400 homeseekers arrived in\nSpokane last night over the Great\nNorthern and Northern Pacific rail-\nways. They come from the middle\nwest-Minnesota. Wisconsin, Iowa,\nIllinois, Indiana and some from the\nDakotas. The work of the booster\nclub is responsible. Its work has\nbeen done we'll in these sections of\nthe country and the numerous re-\nquests for information has been fol-\nlowed by such influx of homeseek-\ners. They were met at the depot\nlast night by representatives of the\n100000 club and shown about the\ncity during their sojourn here."
